channel.title: Client that works with Gazzascape!?
channel.description: Hey, I Spent AGES editing the gazzascape source, and i have the official gazzascape client too but when i try too connect too my vps with the gazzascape client it just dont load up what so ever. But if i use a ip-changer it will load up perfectly but i cant see the items on the server, so is there any other clients i can try for the gazzascape source?
